			"editorData": {
				"HowToTrigger": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Load up CTY_Main_A\r\nuse the debug book to set the IRN prisoners to your desired state (Use Prisoners saved if you want to save the Gondians) \r\nGo to -1933; -7; 205\r\nUse killcombat to defeat the mindflayer and other enemies nearby\r\nUse any means to destroy the big neural machine.\r\nWatch escape cinematic, and have your outcome dialog. Based on your decisions Barcus should usually survive the outcome.\r\nTalk to Barcus after every other gnomes has left."
				},
